Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.80,0:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Guide us, the Children's Crusade, \Nto the Holy Land of Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.32,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this ship going?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it going to the Holy Land of Jerusalem?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.76,0:00:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be sold as slaves\N on the Barbary Coast. {was: Ivory Coast. I wonder who came up with this, like what was there to do on the ivory cost in 1212? at least irl it [supposedly] happened in tunis; I wanted to joke that Americans made this anime, but Americans wouldn't even know about ivory coast or tunis}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.80,0:00:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be a mistake!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.03,0:00:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pope in Rome ordered us \Nto go to Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the leader, Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.16,0:01:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been sold by the Pope.\NWanna see the contract?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.97,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.48,0:01:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.91,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We believed in you. Is this how\Nyou reward our loyalty?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.89,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.89,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann! Pierre!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.23,0:01:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.63,0:01:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Michel!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer believe in God!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.29,0:01:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For my friends who've been betrayed, someday...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.71,0:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I will take revenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.03,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become a fallen angel
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.78,0:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and dispel our humiliation!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard as usual, I see?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Sage!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.74,0:04:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Has there been any change\Nin your wife's condition?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.44,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for her eyes,\Nshe's doing quite well.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.19,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've obtained a good herb.\NI'll come by later.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How peaceful.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.39,0:04:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How truly peaceful.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.33,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Since the Amakusa Restoration, \Nthe world has seen no wars.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if time itself has stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.42,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.49,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The eternal flow of time \Nrushes forth with certainty.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there is no countercurrent...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.00,0:04:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.28,0:04:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. \NJust talking to myself, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, isn't today the commemoration day \Nfor those who served the cause
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Amakusa Restoration, \Nthe St. Michaela Girls' Crusade? {meaning the girls fought on the christians' side and helped stop the persecution of christians so now Japan is the most christian country on earth or something}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, quite right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.78,0:05:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I should also go offer them\Na flower or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.86,0:05:33.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,This world, without national\Nor religious divisions...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,Without wars among peoples...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is the fruit of the Amakusa Restoration,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.70,0:05:45.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,initiated by these Girl Crusaders \Nof St. Michaela School.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,However, what of the erased history,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.99,0:05:53.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,starting from the Restoration, through the Greater East Asia War and the Showa period?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.08,0:05:56.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,Am I the only one that knows\Nthis lost history?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,The Restoration only succeeded \Nbecause they came from that future. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.72,0:06:08.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,Thus, whoever remembers even a shred of the lost timeline must be terminated.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,No matter who it may be. {/how many people/no one}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke... Daisuke was killed in battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Daisuke?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.60,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Died in battle? There's no war anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.11,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shimabara Rebellion \Nwas the last such thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.55,0:07:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Girls' Crusade overturned\Nthe feudal government.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.62,0:07:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the Roman Catholic Church and\N the Holy Roman Empire were also destroyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. No more religions\Nand no more nations.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.70,0:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No more rotten wars that pit\Npeople against each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to "Amakusa Hans" Aiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's gotten into me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All I do is cause you worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.32,0:07:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,every year, when I hear the bell that marks the anniversary of the Restoration,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I get such a headache.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.95,0:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As if some unknown being \Nis shrieking deep inside my head.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.98,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm all right now.\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,Why? Why is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko, how's your wound?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. It's healed a great deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back to my old self soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an embarrassing mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.84,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the uprising at St. Michaela School,\N we've waged war in Amakusa,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then against the feudal army.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought non-stop till we finally \Ntook Edo Castle here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We all take our hats off to you \Nfor charging into the battle first.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's no wonder you got hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Michaela School, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.12,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after all this, \NI can still remember it like yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.75,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late! I'm Mimura Aiko. \NI'm the new transfer student.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some gall\N for a new transfer student. {not the same text as in the first OVA; lit: you've got some nerve, [to be late] right after transferring}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your cross?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dyed hair is against the school rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So are those shoes and socks!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing pierced earrings is an outrage!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's all alike?\NWhat about our personalities?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you defy me, I'll have to discipline you! {OVA 1: Get ready for punishment!}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! An S&M show? {sado-mazo}{OVA 1: Oh, aren't you the sadist? - too liberal for my taste tbh}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit me hard, harder, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, harder! Right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimura!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimura Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.55,0:09:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimura Aiko, you have broken school rules on your first day and rebelled against the sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.44,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, in the name of the Girls' Crusade, \Nwe are going to punish you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.70,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Girls' Crusade, we are going to punish you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.07,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. You guys are kidding, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.04,0:09:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...punish you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...going to punish you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.47,0:09:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe how fierce Rika \Nand everyone were toward me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.62,0:09:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my first acquaintance with Rika and the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.73,0:10:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No sooner did I join the college than I was on display as an example of bad behavior.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.26,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to that, I learned of the Dean's\N right-hand man, Karino Daisuke,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and his conspiracy at St. Michaela.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.33,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to ruin the sublime mission of the Girls' Crusade. You're the Devil!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devil?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the Devil...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the Devil have...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,these on her back?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wing marks...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,An angel?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I confided everything to Rika. {she is saying this now, not in the flashback - maybe it'd be wise to set up an additional subtitles style for flashbacks in this OVA; rika is the girl with the glasses}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her that the transfer student Mimura Aiko
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is an alias for Hans, the leader of the Children's Crusade,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.52,0:11:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and about the tragedy of my fellow crusaders back in 1212.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Similar events are unfolding right now. {talking in the flashback again}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the name of God,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.20,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the Dean claims she's preparing you girls for stardom with the Takarazuka Revue.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.54,0:11:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's a front for\N a secret military mission,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,organized by Karino Daisuke,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.56,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,whereby you will be sent\N to the battlefield as sex slaves:
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the Michaela Project.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie. {I'm tired of looking up those exact lines in OVA1, don't care anymore}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.97,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I showed you proof that I am Hans,\N in spite of being a woman...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.90,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,would you believe me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A hermaphrodite...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.41,0:12:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is born out of freedom.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.43,0:12:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Forced celibacy is but a delusion, \Nmade up in God's name.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an angel?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.92,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the kind of angel \Nthat's been blessed with the grace of God.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fallen angel, here to kill God.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.57,0:13:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I need your help, Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.28,0:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus began our battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Hans Heilner!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, in the battle\N against Shiro of Amakusa... {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amakusa_Shir%C5%8D - shiro is his name, amakusa is the name of the area he came from, the islands south of kyushu}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done on making it here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Shiro Tokisada of Amakusa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring us here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.42,0:14:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In this part of the world, I {\i1}am{\i0} God.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.38,0:14:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight alongside me. Paradise is near. {From Portuguese “paraíso”}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.18,0:14:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come here to kill God. We won't tolerate any god, anywhere in the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.21,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.21,0:14:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you the power of a god!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You fraud!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.22,0:15:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no God. Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.84,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At least...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.46,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die after\N experiencing a first love.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hans...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika... Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.65,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my name? I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.71,0:16:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Together with Hans Aiko,\N Ikeda Rika revolted at St. Michaela
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and died in Amakusa. \NYou're her departed spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Died in Amakusa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.39,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I died?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.42,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean \NI'll never see Aiko or Hans again?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.03,0:16:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Aiko, my first love...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see her?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.00,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see "Amakusa Hans" Aiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.50,0:17:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.37,0:17:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Her eye is internally damaged. {was: back of the pupil }
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, gramps.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.24,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If applying this doesn't heal it,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it might just be incurable.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.24,0:17:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if my eyes ever\Nreturn to normal again.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.02,0:17:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it.\NYou mustn't think like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.63,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your condition, one might say, is psychological.\NIt stems from your own attitude. {one's frame of mind; way one looks at things}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My attitude?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.84,0:17:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something you don't want to see. \NThat's the source of your problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I don't want to see?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Sage, what could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.27,0:18:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't brood over it.\NRight, Yayoi?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.40,0:18:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sooner or later, you will remember. \NJust be patient.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.74,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.54,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... May I ask you one more thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.88,0:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead... {corpse}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.92,0:18:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to raise the dead?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the dead?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.91,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not impossible, \Nbut it certainly is a large undertaking. {Was pain in the neck, felt too jocular}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.91,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can communicate with the dead. {lit: use necromancy; spiritism; spiritualism}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.11,0:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain teenage girl that I recalled.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Ikeda Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.53,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the girl crusaders from St. Michaela.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She died as a martyr during the Shimabara Rebellion.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.44,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the heroes of the Restoration.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.94,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alongside their leader, Amakusa Hans Aiko,\N she became a much respected figure.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on Earth did you recall {\i1}her{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.01,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When I talk to her, I feel as if \NI'm talking with the "me" of old.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.23,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She died before fulfilling her feelings\N for {the person who was }her first love and was unable to pass on. {became a lingering spirit}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.99,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I've consummated my own,\Nthere's another "me" inside. {lit: made my first love come true}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.90,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She has lost her first love\Nand is crying, as it were.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.54,0:19:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you use a particular\Nmediumistic incantation?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.05,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried to revive her, but she only becomes an illusion and then disappears.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.70,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the spirit has no flesh.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Her consciousness is intact,\Nbut her body is long gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's impossible?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.45,0:20:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you don't have the actual body,\Nyou provide a substitute. {replacement flesh}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.26,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's something that could\Nbecome her body.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.80,0:20:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A soulless but mobile doll.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I need to recall the spirit\Nand plant it in the doll?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.98,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only a substitute body,\Nso the spirit won't live long.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Yuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.63,0:21:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One wrong move, \Nand your own soul could be taken.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Humor my one and only wish, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A living and vital ghost. {kinda says "a ghost that lives on in death"}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.58,0:21:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy name is nothingness.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.11,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of nothingness cometh nothingness.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However, nothingness hath life.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.40,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By forces yet unseen,\NI shall bestow life in thee.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Non cogito, ergo non cogito. {lit: without cogito, there's no cogito}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.40,0:21:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Non sum, ergo non sum. {lit: If I am not in the world, I am not.}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.17,0:21:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{wasn't in the officials and I can't make sense of it either, so likely gibberish as well, but if you really want to put something here, the text would "If the night rains and mornings come, the blood will be poured out." - if I just try to combine the proto-words together without trying to make sense of it}If the night raineth and the morning cometh, then blood shall be poured out.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer must thou\Nsleep on a lotus bed?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.32,0:22:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The evening of the Sabbath\Nhath now expired. {over}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.02,0:22:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead, raise thyself slowly,\Nas it is thy wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.46,0:22:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Dear dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.95,0:22:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer wilt thou sleep\Non the bed of Nirvana?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.24,0:22:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The banquet of Sabbath is all but through.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.83,0:22:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,O devil, raise thyself slowly, as it is thy wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.31,0:22:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Dear dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.22,0:23:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Say your name!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.96,0:23:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.73,0:23:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize the name\Nof Amakusa Hans Aiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.03,0:23:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amakusa Hans Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.77,0:23:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The St. Michaela Girls' Crusade...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.18,0:23:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimura Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.58,0:23:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.58,0:23:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.81,0:24:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.10,0:24:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Calm her down, Yayoi!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.41,0:24:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.29,0:24:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimura Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.99,0:24:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.11,0:24:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not a mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.53,0:24:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My memory was not wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.29,0:24:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.37,0:24:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, what are you plotting?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.37,0:24:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to recover the lost memory.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.66,0:24:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.55,0:24:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.58,0:24:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one who told me to remember\N what I don't want to see.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.56,0:24:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I would do anything for it, \Neven give up my soul!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.39,0:24:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:00.40,0:25:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When should I surrender my soul?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.33,0:25:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Time, be still. You are beautiful."
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.87,0:25:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you feel that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.57,0:25:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, be still. You are beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:16.42,0:25:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let you!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.62,0:25:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yayoi.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.53,0:25:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.25,0:25:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.48,0:25:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You evil-natured woman...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.96,0:25:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What you wish to know\Nand are afraid to remember...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.98,0:25:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What lies in the turmoil\Nof conflicting emotions...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:54.38,0:25:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is the other history!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:58.00,0:26:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The other history?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:00.09,0:26:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll have to fight you myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:08.84,0:26:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the other history, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:14.42,0:26:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what really happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.32,0:26:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please answer me, Old Sage.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.86,0:27:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten old. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:25.20,0:27:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda... Rika?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:31.72,0:27:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:36.14,0:27:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika, do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:43.60,0:27:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:51.56,0:27:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue, what's on your mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:54.27,0:27:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing that's on yours, probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.91,0:28:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That our mission isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:00.79,0:28:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When we revolted at St. Michaela, \Nour original plan
Dialogue: 10,0:28:03.67,0:28:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,was to take the time tunnel in the chapel
Dialogue: 10,0:28:07.48,0:28:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and help Hans save\N his fellow crusaders, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:11.25,0:28:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to Rome in 1212?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:13.61,0:28:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do. Aiko's still recovering.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:16.74,0:28:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that. She's spent.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.43,0:28:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can let her rest here awhile.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:22.34,0:28:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean... {eh, then...?}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.60,0:28:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go without her.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:27.31,0:28:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue, don't forget Aiko is Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:30.04,0:28:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're suggesting\N we leave her here and go on our own?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:33.31,0:28:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The St. Michaela Girls' Crusade\N has already proven its worth
Dialogue: 10,0:28:36.13,0:28:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,through its success against the feudal government.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:40.38,0:28:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I... disagree.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.10,0:28:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:46.04,0:28:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Whoever wants\N to stay should stay.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:50.46,0:28:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my group with me. {yukigumi - yuki's group}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:03.13,0:29:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Mayumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:04.87,0:29:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Kozue and her group.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:06.91,0:29:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kozue?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:08.10,0:29:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they left for Rome.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:11.91,0:29:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For Rome?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:40.74,0:29:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.56,0:29:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:53.69,0:29:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:55.92,0:29:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierre.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:57.20,0:29:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:00.82,0:30:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pierre. \NI knew you would volunteer too.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:05.50,0:30:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Marco. Nice to meet you, Pierre.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:08.14,0:30:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:09.24,0:30:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'm gonna be the first to get\N to the Holy Land of Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.48,0:30:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if you can beat me.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.41,0:30:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierre...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:15.60,0:30:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Hans with you guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:18.65,0:30:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:20.44,0:30:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've arrived ahead of us\N to take direct orders from the Pope.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:25.55,0:30:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? He's the leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:28.89,0:30:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the boys in the Holy Roman Empire,\N Hans is the one most devout, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:34.78,0:30:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he's also the most skilled!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:38.75,0:30:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, let me introduce you to Francois\N from the Kingdom of the Franks.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.41,0:30:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Francois. I'm going to prove myself\N just as worthy as you boys. {lit: won't lose to the boys; officials: "I won't be fazed by the male majority!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:48.41,0:30:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a peppy one.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.33,0:30:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to be, to enlist in the Crusade.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:55.59,0:30:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:05.92,0:31:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear children.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:07.67,0:31:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,On this very day, \NI am overjoyed to receive you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:12.03,0:31:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As you already know, there have been many crusades to reclaim Jerusalem,
Dialogue: 10,0:31:18.39,0:31:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been taken away\N from us by the Seljuk Turks.{nope - recaptured by Saladin, who was Kurdish and founder of the Ayyubid Empire}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:22.57,0:31:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, this time, we're going to rely on you children, who are still pure in your hearts.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:28.88,0:31:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One could say, you are angels who have\N been blessed with the grace of God!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:35.25,0:31:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The adults have failed \Nto take back the Holy Land.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:38.56,0:31:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But not you!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:39.92,0:31:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are angels, and therefore,\N God's servants.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:44.36,0:31:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To prove it, you have wings on your backs.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:49.44,0:31:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with little faith may miss them,\N but I can see them!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:53.47,0:31:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This Children's Crusade\N is certain to succeed!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:56.64,0:31:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go directly to Marseilles! {why would they go from rome to marseilles to get to jerusalem lmao??? did they not have an atlas at the studio or something? at least historically it made sense because they came from germany and never went to rome}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:01.32,0:32:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Marseilles is the gateway\N to the Mediterranean Sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.61,0:32:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There, God will answer your pure prayers \Nand part the sea in two.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:12.16,0:32:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just as the Red Sea did for Moses!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:19.50,0:32:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not fear.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord is with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:22.35,0:32:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The parted sea will lead you straight \Nto the Holy Land of Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:26.19,0:32:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It will guide you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:29.85,0:32:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I will introduce you\Nto your leader...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:34.01,0:32:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans Heilner!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:50.74,0:32:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.80,0:32:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:52.60,0:32:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Hans?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:53.81,0:32:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:58.20,0:33:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord will always watch over us.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:02.54,0:33:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we shall win the holy war!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:05.57,0:33:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we shall win the holy war!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:09.60,0:33:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of love and the Holy Ghost, \Nmay glory be with the Children's Crusade!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.82,0:33:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,May glory be with the Children's Crusade!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:28.12,0:33:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone named Gonza wants to see Aiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:31.74,0:33:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:33.75,0:33:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here, Gonza?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:35.85,0:33:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki seems to have awakened.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.03,0:33:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She has?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:40.54,0:33:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she been here?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:42.50,0:33:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:43.39,0:33:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find her.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:45.11,0:33:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she'd definitely\N end up on this side. {lit: I only thought she's in this world - meaning not in michaela, not in 1945 or any other time/timeline}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:48.59,0:33:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could she possibly be?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:51.89,0:33:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be damned!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:53.26,0:33:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:55.26,0:33:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue's group is in danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:58.96,0:34:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to leave!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:00.90,0:34:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:01.93,0:34:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Get everyone ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:03.89,0:34:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're charging into the Holy Roman Empire! {/marching toward}{also no idea how defeating the HRE is supposed to help their cause against the pope lmao, since to quote voltaire, it was neither holy, nor Roman, nor an empire; I understand there was no wikipedia in 1994 but holy shit (put intended), how ignorant can you be? did they literally decide that HRE was where the pope lives because it was called that? lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:39.23,0:34:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:41.27,0:34:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:42.66,0:34:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Misayo?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:45.88,0:34:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Rika. Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:48.48,0:34:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. In Amakusa, she...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:50.92,0:34:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But look!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.21,0:34:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika! You lived?!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:00.49,0:35:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I came to, \NI was being looked after by a fisherman.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:04.86,0:35:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we couldn't find you.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:07.49,0:35:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a bloody war. \NThere were bodies everywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:11.31,0:35:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to tell who was who.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:14.51,0:35:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so glad to see you again!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:17.47,0:35:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I caused you such trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:20.68,0:35:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:24.86,0:35:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how {\i1}did{\i0} you get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:28.99,0:35:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that after going back in time\N to Amakusa, you overthrew the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.32,0:35:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I knew that Aiko, or rather, Hans would bring you here to save his fellows.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:43.87,0:35:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharp thinking as usual, Rika.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.94,0:35:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With Rika, we're unbeatable.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:49.42,0:35:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a boost to our morale!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:52.13,0:35:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:56.89,0:35:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find Mimura Aiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:59.28,0:36:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not there.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:01.02,0:36:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:02.24,0:36:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Takemiya Kozue and her group\Nare headed toward the Vatican. {papal court}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:06.42,0:36:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They are planning to join the Crusade.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:09.40,0:36:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. So that's why.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:12.36,0:36:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:14.16,0:36:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I combine your story with what I know,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:17.44,0:36:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the Amakusa Restoration\N impacted the whole world,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:20.70,0:36:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because Aiko was Hans Heilner,\Nthe leader of the Crusade.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:26.25,0:36:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls of St. Michaela must have led the World Restoration.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:30.81,0:36:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:35.55,0:36:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:37.10,0:36:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you obsess about these things?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:41.56,0:36:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You need only do as I say.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:44.76,0:36:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:45.37,0:36:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But?!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:46.30,0:36:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Rika! You've died once, haven't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:50.53,0:36:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget you owe me\N for reviving you!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:54.61,0:36:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:56.19,0:36:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your second life won't last very long.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:59.53,0:37:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When your mission is complete,\NI'll allow you to live freely.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:04.92,0:37:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will infiltrate the Crusade as one of the soldiers.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:08.34,0:37:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay with the St. Michaela students.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:11.46,0:37:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is my fault\N for leaving it up to Daisuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:15.00,0:37:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I myself had fought,\Nwe wouldn't have lost the war.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:18.76,0:37:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:44.66,0:37:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:54.10,0:37:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Aaron.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:55.40,0:37:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a soldier of the Children's Crusade, Aaron.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:59.68,0:38:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaron?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:26.32,0:38:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we'll finally depart tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:29.06,0:38:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's imperative that you act responsibly! {disciplined}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:31.84,0:38:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already relayed your order.\NDon't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:34.97,0:38:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:37.01,0:38:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking like a real leader, Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:39.65,0:38:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been entrusted with the duty of bringing all of you to the Holy Land of Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:46.06,0:38:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans, did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:48.39,0:38:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Support has arrived from Japan today. {engun - supporting army - they're not exactly an army so idk what to call it. Could use reinforcements, but I am not strongly decided about it.}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:51.07,0:38:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Support?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:52.07,0:38:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They say they're students \Nof St. Michaela School.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:54.67,0:38:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All girls, to boot!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:56.52,0:38:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All girls?\NMust be a courageous bunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:59.92,0:39:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Japan?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:01.59,0:39:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an island nation in the Orient, they say.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.16,0:39:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Is it farther away than Mongolia?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:07.36,0:39:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the one who came here yesterday is also from Japan, isn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:15.09,0:39:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:16.52,0:39:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ikeda Rika, from Japan.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:19.51,0:39:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hans Heilner. \NHow do you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:28.18,0:39:31.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hans... You are Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:31.56,0:39:34.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,But, right now, you don't know me yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:37.92,0:39:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.32,0:39:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here already?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:41.00,0:39:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:42.01,0:39:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We got separated on the way.\NWe were worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:44.72,0:39:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew we would find you here.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:46.84,0:39:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Kozue said.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:49.28,0:39:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce you to my friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:52.51,0:39:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their leader, Hans. \NHans Heilner.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:58.69,0:39:59.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's Hans.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:59.90,0:40:02.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hans before he came to St. Michaela.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:02.32,0:40:04.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,The Hans who doesn't know us.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:05.80,0:40:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Hans?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:07.83,0:40:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You know Hans?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:10.97,0:40:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:12.40,0:40:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Word of Hans has even\Nreached the Orient!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:15.57,0:40:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Michel.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:17.64,0:40:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierre.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:18.84,0:40:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Johann.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:19.84,0:40:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And Marco. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:21.63,0:40:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takemiya Kozue.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:25.25,0:40:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoike Kumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:26.68,0:40:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hagio Misayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:28.68,0:40:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato Watoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:30.19,0:40:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done coming all this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:32.64,0:40:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I must tell you...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:35.16,0:40:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have come all this way
Dialogue: 10,0:40:37.52,0:40:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with the intent of dissuading you from going to Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:41.63,0:40:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you shouldn't\N even go to Marseilles.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:46.40,0:40:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:55.73,0:40:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long, long way to Marseilles.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:58.19,0:41:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be faced with fever\Nand disasters.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:01.57,0:41:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! We're prepared for all trials!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:04.63,0:41:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardship is the path we've chosen.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:06.96,0:41:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the path of love and tribulation \Nthat the Lord preached!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:12.25,0:41:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you support us or not? {support army}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:14.60,0:41:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We do.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:15.64,0:41:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:16.93,0:41:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist on going, \Nwe'll go with you, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:21.41,0:41:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:25.04,0:41:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, this is all we can tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:28.80,0:41:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:34.15,0:41:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go figure.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:35.37,0:41:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Some allies. {lit: unthinkable support army - meaning they came to dissuade them instead of support}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:38.65,0:41:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going with your fellows?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:41.87,0:41:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:43.66,0:41:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What could they be thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:47.57,0:41:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know? {this is still hans speaking to rika off-screen}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:49.46,0:41:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ah... I mean, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:21.57,0:42:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:25.04,0:42:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Aaron.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:27.07,0:42:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've enlisted in the Children's Crusade.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:29.81,0:42:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something very important\Nto tell Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:34.66,0:42:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:43.50,0:42:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:48.66,0:42:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please trust me?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:55.81,0:42:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to hear you first.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:12.98,0:43:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to earn your trust,\N I shall offer you my body.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:22.16,0:43:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 10,0:43:26.96,0:43:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:29.93,0:43:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A hermaphrodite!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:32.88,0:43:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"An eye for an eye" is one\N of the heathen's sayings, naturally.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:37.58,0:43:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I find myself up against vicious treacheries of the Devil's own androgynous servant. {literal though I'm not sure what it's supposed to mean}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:42.60,0:43:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devil's servant?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:43.85,0:43:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devil is coming to hinder\Nthe expedition of the Children's Crusade.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:48.31,0:43:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, \Nyou must get them to Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:52.03,0:43:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, at least, to Marseilles.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:56.37,0:43:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own good...
Dialogue: 10,0:43:57.66,0:44:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What exactly do you know?!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:00.50,0:44:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:02.35,0:44:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why
Dialogue: 10,0:44:04.83,0:44:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am offering my body to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:07.01,0:44:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you take me for?\N I'm the Pope...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:10.65,0:44:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:18.93,0:44:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about your secret pastimes, \NYour Holiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:25.39,0:44:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My lips are sealed.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:27.41,0:44:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please, enjoy my body\Nto your heart's content.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:30.12,0:44:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is on the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:32.13,0:44:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The end justifies the means.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:37.13,0:44:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you... trust you...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:46.46,0:44:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I have to discard this body,
Dialogue: 10,0:44:49.42,0:44:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will consummate my true love.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:53.97,0:45:01.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,Daisuke, I promise you I will bury all the Aiko Mimuras of the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:03.99,0:45:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:04.96,0:45:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have it your way.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:11.40,0:45:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco and his fellows, \Nand our own St. Michaela comrades...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:15.34,0:45:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let them be sold into slavery!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:18.88,0:45:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone,\N to the Holy Roman Empire!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:23.51,0:45:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:26.72,0:45:33.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,For the sake of this world I have finally built, \Nand as long as you don't kill me... and Hans,
Dialogue: 10,0:45:33.44,0:45:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,let's fight, Yuki! {very winded sentence but basically he says "if you want to destroy this new timeline/history I have created where daisuke gets killed, you'll have to kill me"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:49.77,Song,,0,0,0,,{the song is likely "光(yasashisa)につつまれて" by 上田浩恵; couldn't find so much as a mention of it on the internet, let alone any trace of lyrics; translating by ear}The wind blows through the gaps in the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:56.05,Song,,0,0,0,,And the radiance of freedom pours through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:03:00.82,Song,,0,0,0,,I gathered it with both my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:06.17,Song,,0,0,0,,And kept searching until I found my true feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:12.80,Song,,0,0,0,,While seeing gentle dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:26.53,Song,,0,0,0,,Even the days when I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:33.24,Song,,0,0,0,,While staring at the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:44.37,Song,,0,0,0,,Those days no longer exist
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.41,0:46:15.19,Song,,0,0,0,,{Tears are Bells ~櫂 by Torsten Rasch and Ueda Hiroe again; unlike the OP, this one is strangely well preserved and available for official streaming, but still no trace of lyrics; translating by ear }I've been waiting for your hand forever
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.19,0:46:37.04,Song,,0,0,0,,Drowning and sinking in the depths of sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.28,0:46:48.90,Song,,0,0,0,,Freed from all doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.90,0:47:01.89,Song,,0,0,0,,I dream of the time when I could swim freely
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.89,0:47:06.60,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm born again
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.56,0:47:19.86,Song,,0,0,0,,Over the waves, beyond the sea,\N the wind will blow me to the faraway land
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.86,0:47:33.21,Song,,0,0,0,,Let the ship sail away in search of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.46,0:47:45.50,Song,,0,0,0,,{the credits said the english lyrics are by rasch the composer himself}You are best and best I need
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.50,0:47:51.37,Song,,0,0,0,,Taking all the sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.38,0:48:00.11,Song,,0,0,0,,This is the bleeding heart
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.11,0:48:14.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Now the echo starts to rewind here
